    "description_long": "This object is a compact, rectangular radio receiver with a retro design, featuring a brown and gray color scheme. The front face displays a large circular speaker grille on the left, a transparent frequency indicator panel with printed radio bands in the center, and two rectangular buttons or sliders on the right. A black carrying strap is attached to the left side, making it portable and easy to carry. The back panel is mostly flat and dark gray, with subtle horizontal grooves, a small circular port, and a battery compartment. The casing appears to be made of hard plastic, with metallic and electronic components likely housed inside.",
